1.在resources中新建application.yml

server:

  port: 8080

pocket:

  name: guoguo

  age: 26

  address: 长宁区

直接即可，无需转码，文字也不会有乱码的情况

2.在resources中新建application.properties

server.port=8080

pocket.name=guoguo

pocket.age=26

pocket.address=长宁区

通过http://tool.chinaz.com/tools/unicode.aspx网站，将长宁区在线转码为\u957f\u5b81\u533a

即**pocket.address=长宁区**改为*pocket.address=\u957f\u5b81\u533a*
